{"tid":1441692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有抗爭者注意 黑警最新戰術：軍裝+防暴速龍化","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:35:25.000Z","uid":90601,"like":358,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"25a6842ab1826a40576fd9b10a73ef146355a04f","tid":1441692,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"有夢遊經歷既都知 以往差佬多數係<br />\n防暴&gt;&gt;防線&gt;&gt;&gt;黑旗出tg&gt;&gt;&gt;速龍出閘打人拉人<br />\n但回顧今日全局 好明顯tg已放少左 槍無開 尖沙嘴圍狗屋突襲拉人<br />\n由示威者到場 到拉人成個過程快左好多<br />\n唔會再現728之前對峙3,4個鐘既情況<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特別留要意既係<br />\n以往「速龍到場」被視為係黑警全面清場既訊號<br />\n但今日好明顯唔係 連防暴 軍裝 甚至便衣都「速龍化」<br />\n基本只係無拎住長盾既防暴 都衝前拉人打人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n可以簡單總結 就係黑警依家無意「開戰」 只係想大搜捕<br />\n你係唔係真抗爭者都好 好似捉依因咁掂到你 你就48小時<br />\n<br />\n可以點應對?<br />\n首先<br />\n1. <strong>唔好再盲等tg 然後俾滅煙隊救火</strong><br />\n今晚已見 黑警可以舉黑旗 但唔放tg 然後直接突襲拉人 <br />\n黑警知你地唔驚tg 甚至係專登博有tg 所以tg反而成為左弭誘<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 唔好等速龍黎到先走</strong><br />\n依家防暴同便衣可能都受過訓練 知道點樣有隊型衝前拉人 已唔係下下靠速龍<br />\n夠時間就走 唔好戀戰<br />\n幾時夠時間? 好簡單 就係班差佬開始被動 然後互相唔知做乜鳩果陣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警得一個最大弱點: 要等指示 要服從 唔可以個別行動 </span><br />\n依個亦係義士變換場地既最有利時間點<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，大家都要「真 be water」<br />\n<strong>路障可以繼續起</strong> 因為可以阻止到黑警衝前 就算5分鐘都好<br />\n但起完一定要走 一定要be water 包括圍狗屋都係 今晚tst就係血的教訓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無gear既/唔打慣前線既 唔好食花生食太耐 唔好心存僥倖</span><br />\n最近幾次俾人拉既 好多都係街坊 甚至花生友和理非<br />\n唔好覺得告你唔入坐48就算 無必要絕對唔好俾人周到/點相 下次行動風險大好多 亦好多人擔心你<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港"},{"pid":"48cfda3511be055160d82e054e5b485e8cae7a9a","tid":1441692,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8710760a9995d208a9541c4a900d3969a36c2be","tid":1441692,"uid":1099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bc967546eefce863535f9edc9f3dbba56688243","tid":1441692,"uid":207902,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:20:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n今日班狗真係行動快咗好多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb94a45cf59db97d1407d39c35f927667021e0a","tid":1441692,"uid":56485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"大力推！"},{"pid":"114bb44d8628023888fdebb03d957a2aba8d678a","tid":1441692,"uid":48838,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:22:51.000Z","msg":"警察改哂策略<br />\n<br />\n派少量人馬布防罰企<br />\n其他大班人喺車/警署嘆冷氣<br />\nTG快速驅散完又再返車/警署嘆過<br />\n仲有OT claim<br />\n<br />\n撚唔撚到成問題..."},{"pid":"c8a54b55c71884774cc9e553538b0543c4554fc1","tid":1441692,"uid":284630,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:24:28.000Z","msg":"人地外國幾十年防暴反恐經驗, 防暴係要陣形, 部署, 推進<br />\n毅進仔既鳩衝戰術, 唔係以為醒過人地呀<br />\n大家唔好忘記新城市班狗幾撚慘"},{"pid":"0263309d6831f4b2d37dd118d6aae1620af7f3da","tid":1441692,"uid":19002,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"推一推先<br />\n樓主講得好有道理<br />\n當班狗係到呆下呆下果陣就係佢地諗緊計既時候<br />\n依個時候玩轉場佢地就會hang機<br />\n玩得多既話就會有狗唔耐煩，佢地就會出錯<br />\n咁先係真正既be water<br />\n<br />\n其實大家真係要play smart<br />\n今次因為無大台所以差佬無一個單一可靠source去prepare<br />\n我地應該好好咁利用依一點<br />\n利用我地既靈活性去對付佢地"},{"pid":"5ea231e01694dad4831fc97b0235feec8dc5651c","tid":1441692,"uid":90601,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"114bb44d8628023888fdebb03d957a2aba8d678a","tid":1441692,"uid":48838,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:22:51.000Z","msg":"警察改哂策略<br />\n<br />\n派少量人馬布防罰企<br />\n其他大班人喺車/警署嘆冷氣<br />\nTG快速驅散完又再返車/警署嘆過<br />\n仲有OT claim<br />\n<br />\n撚唔撚到成問題..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"論武力 義士一定唔夠黑警打<br />\n義士只能係機動性同體力上面贏到黑警<br />\n<br />\n特別一提係體力 唔好以為黑警真係鐵做<br />\n俾你sdu係 大熱天時全幅武裝今日咁跑法 一樣頂唔順 上次805大把係攰到周街訓<br />\n所以遊擊戰可以放心打 只要範圍夠廣 速度夠快"},{"pid":"425971cce8ad6c152d0b40b9053b11658817cc73","tid":1441692,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f3dda77549724bb99ebf36af81968f88bf66c2","tid":1441692,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95527a0f597d6777031967019d099e1d38d5131c","tid":1441692,"uid":253890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"真心要大力推俾其他人見到，始終手足一個不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb6b091d4e89419da3edf9aeb4773922f450507","tid":1441692,"uid":253890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手動置頂"},{"pid":"21b12756883141a792305637a309d316fed4548f","tid":1441692,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a6842ab1826a40576fd9b10a73ef146355a04f","tid":1441692,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"有夢遊經歷既都知 以往差佬多數係<br />\n防暴&gt;&gt;防線&gt;&gt;&gt;黑旗出tg&gt;&gt;&gt;速龍出閘打人拉人<br />\n但回顧今日全局 好明顯tg已放少左 槍無開 尖沙嘴圍狗屋突襲拉人<br />\n由示威者到場 到拉人成個過程快左好多<br />\n唔會再現728之前對峙3,4個鐘既情況<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特別留要意既係<br />\n以往「速龍到場」被視為係黑警全面清場既訊號<br />\n但今日好明顯唔係 連防暴 軍裝 甚至便衣都「速龍化」<br />\n基本只係無拎住長盾既防暴 都衝前拉人打人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n可以簡單總結 就係黑警依家無意「開戰」 只係想大搜捕<br />\n你係唔係真抗爭者都好 好似捉依因咁掂到你 你就48小時<br />\n<br />\n可以點應對?<br />\n首先<br />\n1. <strong>唔好再盲等tg 然後俾滅煙隊救火</strong><br />\n今晚已見 黑警可以舉黑旗 但唔放tg 然後直接突襲拉人 <br />\n黑警知你地唔驚tg 甚至係專登博有tg 所以tg反而成為左弭誘<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 唔好等速龍黎到先走</strong><br />\n依家防暴同便衣可能都受過訓練 知道點樣有隊型衝前拉人 已唔係下下靠速龍<br />\n夠時間就走 唔好戀戰<br />\n幾時夠時間? 好簡單 就係班差佬開始被動 然後互相唔知做乜鳩果陣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警得一個最大弱點: 要等指示 要服從 唔可以個別行動 </span><br />\n依個亦係義士變換場地既最有利時間點<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，大家都要「真 be water」<br />\n<strong>路障可以繼續起</strong> 因為可以阻止到黑警衝前 就算5分鐘都好<br />\n但起完一定要走 一定要be water 包括圍狗屋都係 今晚tst就係血的教訓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無gear既/唔打慣前線既 唔好食花生食太耐 唔好心存僥倖</span><br />\n最近幾次俾人拉既 好多都係街坊 甚至花生友和理非<br />\n唔好覺得告你唔入坐48就算 無必要絕對唔好俾人周到/點相 下次行動風險大好多 亦好多人擔心你<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"314ba89e2ce0a801016e7e38ff19e88570fa160a","tid":1441692,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6a129bb664c9cb5e9e197187acd8a34e15c30d","tid":1441692,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:34:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43187030ce11def8a01989cc008f141c496b54c","tid":1441692,"uid":215794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"25a6842ab1826a40576fd9b10a73ef146355a04f","tid":1441692,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"有夢遊經歷既都知 以往差佬多數係<br />\n防暴&gt;&gt;防線&gt;&gt;&gt;黑旗出tg&gt;&gt;&gt;速龍出閘打人拉人<br />\n但回顧今日全局 好明顯tg已放少左 槍無開 尖沙嘴圍狗屋突襲拉人<br />\n由示威者到場 到拉人成個過程快左好多<br />\n唔會再現728之前對峙3,4個鐘既情況<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特別留要意既係<br />\n以往「速龍到場」被視為係黑警全面清場既訊號<br />\n但今日好明顯